<section id="treatments" class="treatments">
  <h2>Treatments & Prices</h2>

  <h3>Injectable Treatments</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Anti-wrinkle:</strong> 1 area £160, 2 areas £215, 3 areas £270  
      <p>Designed to smooth fine lines and create a refreshed, natural look by gently relaxing facial muscles. Common areas: forehead, frown lines, and crow’s feet. Results develop within 3–5 days, lasting around 3 months.</p>
      <p><em>Aftercare:</em> Avoid touching treated areas for 24 hours, remain upright for 4 hours, avoid exercise, saunas, and alcohol for 24 hours.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Lip Flip:</strong> £120  
      <p>A subtle enhancement that relaxes muscles around the upper lip to create a slightly fuller, lifted appearance.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Chin Enhancement:</strong> £150  
      <p>Improves balance and contour using precise filler application to enhance definition while maintaining a natural look.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Natural Lip Filler:</strong> £100 / 0.5ml  
      <p>Add volume and hydration while keeping a soft, natural look. Ideal for shaping and defining lips.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>B12 Injection:</strong> £40  
      <p>Quickly boosts vitamin B12 levels, supporting energy, skin, hair, nails, and mood. Delivered via intramuscular injection for fast absorption.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Hayfever Injection:</strong> £80  
      <p>Contains triamcinolone acetonide, a corticosteroid that reduces inflammation and relieves hay fever symptoms. Not a first-line treatment.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Facial Treatments</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Hydradermabrasion:</strong> £90 (block of 5 £360)  
      <p>Multi-step, non-invasive facial that deeply cleanses, exfoliates, and hydrates. Uses vortex suction and serums to improve acne, fine lines, and tone. Book 5 for the price of 4 — treatments recommended every 4–6 weeks.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>24K Gold Facial:</strong> £50  
      <p>Infused with pure gold to brighten, firm, and hydrate. Boosts collagen, calms redness, and enhances glow. Perfect pre-event treatment.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Dermaplaning:</strong> £35  
      <p>Removes dead skin and peach fuzz for smooth, radiant skin and flawless makeup application.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Globe Facial:</strong> £33  
      <p>Cooling ice globes reduce puffiness, redness, and inflammation while tightening and refreshing the skin.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Define Beauty Facial:</strong> £29  
      <p>Includes cleansing, exfoliating, and moisturizing to deeply refresh and rejuvenate your skin.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Indian Head Massage:</strong> 30 mins £30 / 45 mins £40  
      <p>Ancient Ayurvedic massage focusing on scalp, neck, and shoulders to release tension, improve circulation, and promote relaxation and hair health.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Eye & Brow Treatments</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Brow Wax:</strong> £8  
      <p>Shape and define brows using gentle, precise waxing techniques that enhance your natural features.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Brow Tint:</strong> £10  
      <p>Add depth and definition with a custom tint for fuller, more polished brows. Results last 4–6 weeks.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Brow Wax & Tint:</strong> £18  
      <p>Combine both shaping and tinting for perfectly framed, defined brows lasting up to 6 weeks.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Lash Tint:</strong> £10  
      <p>Darken and define lashes for a naturally enhanced look without mascara.</p>
    </li>

    <li><strong>Lash Lift & Tint:</strong> £19  
      <p>Lifts lashes from the root for longer, fuller appearance; includes tint for added color and definition. Results last 6–8 weeks.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

